# EmailJS configuration for the Contact form.
# 1. Create a free account at https://www.emailjs.com
# 2. Add an Email Service (e.g. Gmail) and an Email Template.
#    In the template body, reference {{from_email}}, {{reply_to}} and {{message}}.
# 3. Copy the IDs/key below, then rename this file to ".env.local".
#
# Until these are set, the Contact form falls back to opening the
# visitor's email client (mailto:) — it still works, just less seamless.

VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=your_service_id
VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=your_template_id
VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=your_public_key
